    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six with its signature 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen boasts a reinforced subframe and documented preventative rod bearing replacement. The valvetrain is precisely tuned with a recent shim adjustment, and the individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous throttle response. Power is channeled through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains taut with factory-spec bushings and McPherson strut/multi-link suspension geometry, preserving the telepathic handling characteristics of the platform. Finished in Carbon Black with zero oxidative degradation and a pristine Nappa leather interior, this is a turn-key mechanical masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
